    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, I think I get the basic idea now. But it feels a bit harder to actually measure in real life. Like, how do you actually quantify those \"lost\" benefits when you're making the decision? Is there a specific way to put a number on the stuff you *didn't* do?",
